  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881590/extras/8365c84d9a885e17c99396fb0e07c3ae.poster.avif?t=1771855865\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881590/extras/8365c84d9a885e17c99396fb0e07c3ae.webm?t=1771855865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881590/extras/8365c84d9a885e17c99396fb0e07c3ae.mp4?t=1771855865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>PropFight</strong> is a 2D physics-based fighting game where you play random props in random arenas where random events occur. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer (online is only supported with Remote Play)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highly customizable game settings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>80 arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>10 props</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>10 events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam workshop support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Input support (fallback to classic input support is possible)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modding is officially supported  using the <strong>Godot Engine</strong> and our development tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881590/extras/8365c84d9a885e17c99396fb0e07c3ae.poster.avif?t=1771855865\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881590/extras/8365c84d9a885e17c99396fb0e07c3ae.webm?t=1771855865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881590/extras/8365c84d9a885e17c99396fb0e07c3ae.mp4?t=1771855865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>PropFight</strong> is a 2D physics-based fighting game where you play random props in random arenas where random events occur. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer (online is only supported with Remote Play)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highly customizable game settings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>80 arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>10 props</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>10 events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam workshop support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Input support (fallback to classic input support is possible)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modding is officially supported  using the <strong>Godot Engine</strong> and our development tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
